channeldata.description: python-anyconfig is a python library provides common APIs to load and dump configuration files in various formats with some useful features such as contents merge, templates, query, schema validation and generation support.  - Home: https://github.com/ssato/python-anyconfig - Author: Satoru SATOH <satoru.satoh@gmail.com> - License: MIT - Document: http://python-anyconfig.readthedocs.org/en/latest/ - Download: PyPI (https://pypi.python.org/pypi/anyconfig) or Copr RPM repos ( https://copr.fedoraproject.org/coprs/ssato/python-anyconfig/)
channeldata.summary: Library provides common APIs to load and dump configuration files in various formats
